==紀念==
2015年，斯維爾德洛夫斯克州地方歷史博物館的門口設立了一座克勒爾奇的半身銅像，銅像在博物館創立145週年的紀念活動中揭幕，以紀念克勒爾奇對自然科學研究的貢獻<ref>{{cite web |title=В центре Екатеринбурга поставили памятник швейцарцу, который создал самый большой краеведческий музей Урала |url=https://www.e1.ru/news/spool/news_id-424365.html |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2018-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922211551/https://www.e1.ru/news/spool/news_id-424365.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://goingrus.com/info/en/russian-cities/sightseeing-in-yekaterinburg/monuments-in-yekaterinburg|title=Monuments in Yekaterinburg|publisher=GoingRus|access-date=2020-11-30|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117220700/https://goingrus.com/info/en/russian-cities/sightseeing-in-yekaterinburg/monuments-in-yekaterinburg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
